snippet.title: Life is Feudal: MMO Highlights - The Tournament | Vanirs Krigsmen
snippet.description:
There was a battle. A battle for glory and honor.

At the end of the third CBT, a party of knights and adventurers decided to hold a tournament in order to celebrate the finished construction of a great castle. And we’ve made a short reportage so you all could join the party too!

Begin your feudal journey: https://play.lifeisfeudal.com/
